- cs.TL (Type Theory) is another possible category because the paper deals with dependent types and higher-order rewrite rules, which are central concepts in type theory. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a less likely category, but still possible because the paper discusses the generalization of abstract data types, which is a software engineering concept. 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is also a less likely category, but possible because the paper deals with pattern-matching, which is a concept used in formal language theory.
